                +------------------------------+
                |         RAW DATA INPUT       |
                |------------------------------|
                | - Candidates (CV, metadata)  |
                | - Jobs (JD, skills, etc.)    |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
                +------------------------------+
                |    VECTOR GENERATION LAYER   |
                |------------------------------|
                | For Candidates & Jobs:       |
                |  - Semantic Embeddings       |
                |  - Structured Features       |
                |  - Unified Vector (112 dim)  |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
                +------------------------------+
                |          CLUSTERING          |
                |------------------------------|
                | Candidate Clustering (KMeans)|
                | Job Clustering (KMeans)      |
                | Stores:                      |
                |  - Cluster Centers           |
                |  - Membership for each item  |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
                +------------------------------+
                |     CLUSTER CORRELATION      |
                |------------------------------|
                | Compute cosine similarity     |
                | between JobClusters &        |
                | CandidateClusters → Matrix    |
                |                              |
                |  Correlation[jc][cc]         |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
                +------------------------------+
                |     MATCHING ENGINE          |
                |------------------------------|
                | For a given Job or JobMeta:  |
                |  1. Build job vector         |
                |  2. Find nearest JobCluster  |
                |  3. Get correlated           |
                |     CandidateClusters        |
                |  4. Pull candidates          |
                |  5. Compute similarity       |
                |  6. Sort and filter          |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
                +------------------------------+
                |      AUTO-SOURCE AGENT       |
                |------------------------------|
                | - Set status=Recommended     |
                | - Save JobCandidateMatch     |
                | - Expose via API / CLI       |
                +--------------+---------------+
                               |
                               v
              +----------------------------------+
              |     OUTPUT (API / UI Layer)      |
              |----------------------------------|
              | /api/match-candidates/           |
              | → Returns best-fit candidates    |
              |   with similarity scores         |
              +----------------------------------+


Please follow setup.sh to setup locally